<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>Telas monitoring</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Montserrat, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #111519;">
<p><strong>Smart plug alert</strong></p>
<p>Monitor / target: ${monitorAddress}</p>
<p>Box IP: ${boxIp}</p>
<p>Incident: ${incidentType} (severity ${severity})</p>
<p>Relay on: ${relayOn} — Power (W): ${powerWatts}</p>
<p>Details: ${hypothesis}</p>
<p>Time: ${notifiedAt}</p>
</body>
</html>
